text: Rastatt is a town in the district of Rastatt in Baden-Württemberg in Germany. It is about southwest of Karlsruhe. == Twin towns – sister cities == Rastatt is twinned with: * Fano, Italy * Guarapuava, Brazil * New Britain, United States * Orange, France * Ostrov, Czech Republic * Woking, England, United Kingdom == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Towns in Baden-Württemberg Category:Rastatt (district)
